narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Confident Care Corp is a Home Health provider based in Hackensack, NJ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $115.1M in Medicaid payments across 1.3M claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $115.1M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 14,385 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
